reviews.customers_say: Customers find the sweater well-made, soft, and beautiful, appreciating its nice color and considering it good value for money. The fit and size receive mixed feedback - while some say it's true to size, others mention it runs a little big. Comfort is also mixed, with some finding it comfortable while others describe it as super itchy.

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars True to size, soft, medium weight, ample turtleneck. A steal for the money!!
items.body: These sweaters are amazing! They are not weight not too heavy and beautiful! True to size, ample turtleneck and I couldn’t be more pleased!! Am going to order more colors!! I ordered the blue and camel. Wonderful fit and for $9.99??? Are you kidding??? My winter wardrobe is done!!!! Incredibly soft as well! Read more
items.author: denise anderson

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Love Turtlenecks!!
items.body: Very reasonable and the perfect turtleneck! Love the color and material! Go for it, especially under Jackets or Blazers! Read more
items.author: Margaret Compagnola

items.title: 4.0 out of 5 stars Great sweater!
items.body: This is a wonderful sweater and fits perfectly, only thing is the sleeves need to be a little tighter around the wrists. Everything else is great! Color is excellent and didn’t fade when I washed it. Read more
items.author: Gail

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Sweater
items.body: The sweater is nice and soft and the size is just right. I will definitely buy another one. Read more
items.author: AA

items.title: 3.0 out of 5 stars Very nice sweater, but long and runs big…
items.body: It seems like it’s hard to find acrylic sweaters anymore, and the acrylic ones are the only ones warm enough for me in the winter, so I was thrilled to find these. They are well-made and 100% acrylic and a nice high but soft neck. All of the pictures show the sweater tucked in so it was hard to tell how long it is and it is long. If you want to wear it with leggings or skinny jeans, here you go. But I was looking for a sweater that was not long, just average length to wear with straight and boot cut jeans and this is too much sweater for those jeans. The length on me hits below upper thigh.Also, it runs a little big. I’m 5’6”, average frame and usually by a large in sweaters, but this one fits like extra large, so too big and sloppy on me and not what I was looking for so will return. Read more
items.author: Mari500

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Comfortable Sweater
items.body: I love this sweater. I like the fit and soft feel of it. The color is a pretty wine shade. I just wish they had it in other colors I needed. Read more
items.author: Patty B.

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Will buy more

items.title: 1.0 out of 5 stars Poor quality
items.body: Arrived flatter than a piece of paper and misshapen. It stunk and felt like it was coated in some sort of chemical/grease. Read more

short_description:
Womens Maxi Dress Long Sleeve is made for a polished look that still feels comfortable to wear. It is designed to sit cleanly on the body with a flattering shape that works for day plans and dressier moments without feeling overdone.

The fit focuses on balance rather than extremes, so you can move naturally while still getting a defined silhouette. Choose your usual size for a closer look, or size up if you prefer a little more ease through the waist and hips.

Styling is simple: keep accessories minimal for a clean finish, or add a jacket and statement shoes when you want a sharper outfit. This piece photographs well thanks to smooth lines and a structured feel that stays put once you have it adjusted.

With the right fit and simple styling, this item becomes an easy go-to when you want something that looks intentional without requiring extra effort.

This piece transitions well from daytime plans to evening events with a quick change of shoes and a small bag or clutch.

If you are between sizes, choose based on how close you like the fit through the waist and hips, then adjust with your usual layering choices.

long_description:
Womens Maxi Dress Long Sleeve is a versatile piece you can reach for when you want a put-together look that still feels comfortable. The goal is simple: a silhouette that reads polished, photographs well, and stays wearable for a full day or a long night.

Fit and sizing Fit is where most outfits win or lose. This design aims for a balanced shape with a defined line through the torso, a clean waist, and a smooth finish through the hips and legs. If you prefer a more relaxed feel, size up; if you like a closer fit, stay true to size. Sizes may include: XS, S, M, L, XL.

Fabric and comfort Comfort is not just about softness. It is also about movement and how the fabric behaves as you walk, sit, and stand. A fabric blend with a bit of give helps it keep its shape while still feeling wearable.

Highlights A clean neckline and a refined silhouette for an elevated look. Designed to layer easily with jackets, wraps, or sweaters. Works well with both minimal accessories and statement pieces.

How to style Styling ideas: keep it minimal with neutral shoes and one standout accessory. For a relaxed daytime look, add a denim jacket or cardigan. For events, switch to a bolder shoe and a small clutch for a sharper finish.

Color notes Available colors may include: Brown, Misty Blue, Off-white, Beige, Deep Orange, Army Green, Black. If a shade is sold out, check back as availability can change.

Care Care guidance matters if you want it to keep its shape and finish. Follow the label first.
